{"tid":302862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)伊拉克宣布全面解放摩蘇爾 IS已經終結","createTime":"2017-06-29T17:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T14:28:56.000Z","uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f108c61457bec10fe35f367b8b87357a8f4ade3c","tid":302862,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"伊拉克國防部宣布已從&ldquo;伊斯蘭國&rdquo;恐怖組織手中全面解放摩蘇爾市。<br />\n<br />\n解放摩蘇爾的戰鬥2016年10月打響。據聯合行動指揮部29日早些時候消息，伊拉克軍隊將&ldquo;伊斯蘭國&rdquo;武裝分子從摩蘇爾市中心擊退。<br />\n<br />\n武裝分子不久前在此炸毀了古老的努裡清真寺。<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克國防部聲明稱：&ldquo;摩蘇爾沒有一個區還在&lsquo;伊斯蘭國&rsquo;的控制下。武裝分子除投降外別無他途。&lsquo;伊斯蘭國&rsquo;在伊拉克的存在永遠結束了。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"854626bd3d51de4064359a49890f9a248995980a","tid":302862,"uid":37822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"6f3e12d21c5ee6737dfbabd1389d0128cc26ee31","tid":302862,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"Syria 呢？<br />\n仲以為成個isis 收左皮"},{"pid":"271c16d3ddaedb3ccfc7114ad72b43eeab7d410c","tid":302862,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Syria 呢？<br />\n仲以為成個isis 收左皮</blockquote><br />\n拉卡仲未失守"},{"pid":"53e8c79f058fed2f3e42f83066ba6484309e9eb8","tid":302862,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa8238a8280f0b4eaa3100fc758561f72829c36","tid":302862,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76d479477d0f709590d3b03af2350efa137eeb8","tid":302862,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:28